metadata.name: Swan Song
metadata.description: After two years away, Nigel returned for four races of the 1994 season. This was the race suit he wore during the Australian Grand Prix which would be his final victory in Formula 1. After claiming a surprise pole position, he was able to capitalize on the controversial collision between title rivals Damon Hill and Michael Schumacher, to score the win and secure the Constructors' Championship for Williams.
